{"tid":1678522,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國FBI格鬥術訓練教程，人體的要害部位！","createTime":"2019-10-27T16:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T07:21:24.000Z","uid":222970,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d65655f0c85aff07988e847fed0b85083681b70b","tid":1678522,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"私了手足係時候要溫下書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bkOu0CtHRdA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbkOu0CtHRdA&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4SwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=37984353\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bkOu0CtHRdA</a>"},{"pid":"09fd99aa8a5a1e4fbb2d32ae5e3f61baf4bf1c7a","tid":1678522,"uid":201414,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:48:25.000Z","msg":"私鳥最緊係清左班左膠撚 夠啦夠啦真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626ee54b4f8a0931bf7880dddf9d032e8eeda5df","tid":1678522,"uid":134141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:49:41.000Z","msg":"想學格鬥術 有冇巴打有推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe08cb2f7206cfdd1834ab1d756949e5e931b10","tid":1678522,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:52:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線，兩面夾擊！</span></span></strong><br />\n抵抗中國魔掌，需要你課金支持！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一、遊說戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中共一直斥巨資，僱用遊說集團在華盛頓進行統戰，收賣美國政客及團體，左右美國政策和輿論。單是華為2019年第3季的遊說支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。</span><br />\n<strong>組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4SwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=e6962447\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4SwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=727ed83f\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4SwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=edd74c24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"a824a50f4225f2eee171becb11d6c334f1c901c6","tid":1678522,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:03:57.000Z","msg":"有用"},{"pid":"cf7eeaf144870f0bd814a20a4046d0ef061ede80","tid":16